      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values value over perfection, but it offers a solid opportunity for commuting, a first car, or a backup vehicle. A sensible choice with room to make it your own.",
