    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to pick up a cheap driver or project for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. It\u2019s being sold as a straightforward, budget-friendly option and could suit a handy buyer, first-time tinkerer, or anyone needing inexpensive transport. If you want something honest, approachable, and priced to move, come take a look.",
