      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Runs, moves, and offers a strong foundation for someone who knows their way around a wrench. This is a straight-up budget driver/project with a durable powertrain layout, honest wear, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it appealing for restoration, parts support, or daily-use rehab. Not a showroom piece, but it has real potential for the right buyer looking for an affordable entry point with usable bones. Priced to reflect condition while leaving room for the next owner to add value.",
      "price": 7900.0,
